snippet: The U.S. Supreme Court on Tuesday blocked key parts of a 2013 law in Texas that had closed all but eight facilities providing abortions in America's second most-populous state....

headline.print_headline: Justices Stop Parts of Texas Abortion Law
headline.main: Justices Stop Parts of Texas Abortion Law

lead_paragraph: The U.S. Supreme Court on Tuesday blocked key parts of a 2013 law in Texas that had closed all but eight facilities providing abortions in America's second most-populous state.
